sourcesContent:
let container = {
  overflowY: "scroll",
  overflowX: "hidden",
  position: "absolute", 
  width: "34vw", 
  height: "85.4vh", 
  left: "65.5vw",
  top: "13vh",
}

let focusedItemTitleContainer = {
  width: "calc(34vw - 17px)", 
  height: "27px",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  color: "white",
  fontSize: "17px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "3px",
  display: "flex",
  flexDirection: "row",
}

let focusedItemTitle = {
  width: "50%",
}

let focusedItemDD = {
  width: "calc(34vw - 19px)", 
  height: "769px",
  borderWidth: "0px 1px 1px 1px",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  position: "relative",
  backgroundColor: "#e8fefd",
}

let focusClose = {
  userSelect: "none",
  fontSize: "25px", 
  position: "absolute",
  left: "32vw",
  paddingRight: "18px",
  cursor: "pointer",
  transform: "rotate(45deg)"
}

let divider = {
  margin: "3px 0px 2px 30px", 
  height: "1px", 
  width: "11.75vw", 
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC"
}

export {
  container,
  focusedItemTitleContainer,
  focusedItemTitle,
  focusedItemDD,
  focusClose,
  divider
}
